text: Thy shadow, Earth, from Pole to Central Sea,&& Now steals along upon the Moon's meek shine
Now steals along upon the Moon's meek shine%% In even monochrome and curving line
In even monochrome and curving line%% Of imperturbable serenity.
Of imperturbable serenity.&& How shall I link such sun-cast symmetry
How shall I link such sun-cast symmetry%% With the torn troubled form I know as thine,
With the torn troubled form I know as thine,&& That profile, placid as a brow divine,
That profile, placid as a brow divine,&& With continents of moil and misery?
With continents of moil and misery?&& And can immense Mortality but throw
And can immense Mortality but throw%% So small a shade, and Heaven's high human scheme
So small a shade, and Heaven's high human scheme%% Be hemmed within the coasts yon arc implies?
Be hemmed within the coasts yon arc implies?&& Is such the stellar gauge of earthly show,
Is such the stellar gauge of earthly show,&& Nation at war with nation, brains that teem,
Nation at war with nation, brains that teem,&& Heroes, and women fairer than the skies?
